{
  "stem": "9943.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the meantime, the job consisted of that we thought that the Germans are going to use-- to use gas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were making masks for the children in case there would be-- because they started to bomb Warsaw right away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was-- How did you experience--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--September 1st, Friday, the Germans attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were bombing the city the same day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was going to work to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, well, it-- well, initially, the first day, one didn't know yet what-- how-- what kind of a form it will take.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On Sunday, the 3rd of September, the French and the English also-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, they did declare war with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went-- that was one time I went to some demonstration to the French embassy and the German-- the French and the English embassies, to demonstrate support.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just to, like, to be-- so grateful we were that they also decided to take part in that war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, of course, one thought that they will do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the meantime, however, there was more bombing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the hospital, we were busy preparing for gas from-- for the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I had to tell this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she used to use me also when she-- this-- the director of the hospital used to send me to some patients sometimes when they called for a doctor, pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she used to-- so-- to patronize me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
